text: Jolly Fellows (), also translated as Happy-Go-Lucky Guys, Moscow Laughs and Jazz Comedy, is a 1934 Russian musical comedy movie directed by Grigori Aleksandrov and starring Lyubov Orlova, Leonid Utyosov, Valentin Parnakh. It was distributed by Mosfilm. ==Other websites== * * Category:1934 comedy movies Category:1934 musical movies Category:Russian comedy movies Category:Russian musical movies Category:Movies directed by Grigori Aleksandrov
